            <td colspan="2" class="titulo2" valign="top">The Man Who Stood Still<span
 class="texto2">
 
 <br>by<br> <a href="../../issue2/aamer_hussein/bio.php"
 class="link3"> Aamer Hussein</a><br><br><br>
</td>
